<br>
The cleric nerf has not prevented our guild from owning VP, Dain, Klandicar/Zlandicar, and clearing out most of Sleeper's Tomb (Master of Guard fell to 17 of us), but the nerf remains annoying.  Clerics die more often, slows up hunts, annoys clerics, etc.  An adjustment back on aggro will be appreciated not only for tactical reasons, but also in order to try and get some of our clerics back playing.  I am hearing of problems in many big guilds now with lack of clerics as they all leave disillusioned.<br>
<br>
Boils down to when the inflow of new content slows and gets outweighed by frustration (nerfs) and boredom, the end is near.  W/o major patches with new content soon, I can fully understand why some of the game's most accomplished players might move on.<br>
<br>
Sadly, EQ will suffer when they do.  FoH's accomplishments have served as the 'carrot on the stick' for many across all servers, giving folks a vision of things to come for them, and a reason to press on.  FoH's accomplishments by default indicate a very talented GROUP of people, so even if Furor leaves I assume FoH will continue kicking ass, but Furor's colorful personality and leadership, not only for FoH but for all of EQ players looking to own the ubers, will be missed.</td></tr></table><br><p>[ No Comments Allowed for Anonymous, please <a href="user.php">register</a>  | <a href="comments.php?sid=111&pid=626&mode=&order=&thold=">Parent</a> ]</font><p><ul><li><a href="comments.php?op=showreply&tid=684&sid=111&pid=674&mode=&order=&thold=#684">Re: Get ready for it.</a> by Anonymous <font size=2>on Monday, March 05 @ 12:45:38 EST</font><br><ul><li><a href="comments.php?op=showreply&tid=689&sid=111&pid=684&mode=&order=&thold=#689">Lemme think of an analogy..</a> by SssornParadigm <font size=2>on Monday, March 05 @ 14:02:25 EST</font><br><li><a href="comments.php?op=showreply&tid=690&sid=111&pid=684&mode=&order=&thold=#690">New Content.. Content gone.</a> by Creediki <font size=2>on Monday, March 05 @ 14:08:30 EST</font><br></ul></ul></p></td><td bgcolor=ffffff><img src=themes/NukeNews/pixel.gif width=10 height=1 border=0></td></tr></table>

